      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 1994 Nissan Skyline GT-R (R32) preserved in its original factory configuration. The RB26DETT twin-turbocharged inline-six displays exceptional health, with bore-scope confirmed cylinder wall integrity and consistent compression across the bank. The ATTESA E-TS torque-split system and Super HICAS four-wheel steering function flawlessly, providing the precise lateral grip these icons are known for. The drivetrain is anchored by a 5-speed manual gearbox with perfectly indexed synchros and a robust limited-slip differential. Every suspension component remains within factory tolerances, featuring original bushings and a chassis entirely free of structural oxidation or stress fatigue. This vehicle maintains its factory-specified boost maps and original ceramic-wheeled Garrett T28 turbos, ensuring a linear power band and authentic driving dynamics. A rare, turn-key specimen for the purist; pre-purchase inspections at any performance specialist are welcomed to verify its mechanical excellence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
